Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷蒙老闆也怪可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都被關在大牢裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是人質
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能讓他忍耐一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火控系統這樣設定可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你寫的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅長做這類工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堪稱完美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了我半天時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本還沒什麼信心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這工作交給專家也要花三天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪學的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？這誰都會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是跟誰學的這門技術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜美 你該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不可能跟泰莎 千鳥一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非是地圖畫錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是地下擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為會把我們帶到多凶險的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是個窮鄉僻壤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對面有個古代遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是在那裡舉行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你在這裡乘上機體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西北方向3公里處有個遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到那裡去待命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離得這麼遠 連遠程指令都收不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為你們的安全著想 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟一發流彈就會釀成大慘劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您安排得真周到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AS的武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遺跡那邊備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於你今晚的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們安排了一台有意思的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多加小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔心的不是你 是機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是不要逞強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要四肢健全地回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打完之後記得請我吃飯喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 你要吃什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他技術高超
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反倒覺得我們的處境比較危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己先開喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 克拉瑪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您來得可真早呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是不喜歡這種拖拖拉拉的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也實屬無奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟全世界的幹部們都將觀賞這場決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不嫌棄 請嘗嘗這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是頂級貨色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在戒煙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到真正的競技場 十字弩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些就是你的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以隨意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}（無法使用）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個觀賞席被設定為無法攻擊狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我今晚的對手在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員還在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭氧味！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經察覺到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是M9
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據我所知 那是你往常最精通的機型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你還身處秘銀的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你查得一清二楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟你頂著真名就在這裡大顯身手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想查不到也難呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然直接在大街上把你處理掉也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那樣太無趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會難得 就決定讓你和M9打一場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是汞合金的主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果能活下來 告訴你也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就憑那坨破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備怎麼應對這架最新兵器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換句話說 這根本就不是比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是行刑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是M9
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是連美軍都沒配備的最新機體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但錯不了 那就是M9
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 我們這邊只是野蠻人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:17.90,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1880,45)}該死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根本就是讓小貨車跟保時捷競賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 就算是地下擂台 這也太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即叫停比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 換地方了 上車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待會聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那坨破爛還真能堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等技術再加上強弩兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也難怪我們對付不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強弩兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 反正不要掉以輕心就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他無非就是一名隨處可見的少年傭兵罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小瞧他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九龍和蓋茨都死在了他的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九龍？蓋茨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然不認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鄉下就是安逸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我們計劃把相良的同伴也處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問您要看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對射是沒有勝算的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 為什麼要分開走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 別戳行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,養豬場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排隊上樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑吧 這再怎麼說也太過了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別給我們找事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們來真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我們一馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很同情你們 不過這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了心排隊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是應該在牢裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別問了 先蹲下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不清楚是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒想到你居然敢大搖大擺地露面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也跟他們一起變成豬飼料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮壓完畢 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了 巴代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷蒙 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自稱記者是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我不能說得太詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來宗介正在接近他的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個目標大概和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一個彈夾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是準備做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子彈所剩無幾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱錘也只剩下兩枚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搏一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往前一點…沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平…平手？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是事故 是他故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M9是純電力驅動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦超過額定負重就無法靈活運作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而野蠻人雖然是舊型號機體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它蛋型的軀體抗壓能力更強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還混用了油壓驅動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被大量瓦礫壓住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它也能憑自身力量逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好機體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 居然讓他給贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能 他到底是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經知道我們的身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定會盡全力來抓你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呀 沒錯 還有你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能打敗這架M9
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該由我來提問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這部機體在與你的戰鬥中出了不少故障
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會不小心把你捏碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很燙是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這架機體的冷卻系統很差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱度都傳到指尖來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我投降 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出你的姓名和組織
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喬治·拉布洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在隸屬於汞合金的侵略部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前是秘銀的士兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前在西太平洋戰隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪會對M9的弱點瞭如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是地中海戰隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的部隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我外出執行任務期間全軍覆沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一無所知地回到基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才發現基地已經被他們佔領了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是你就投降了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總比白白送死要好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的行動據點在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親眼見過的只有的黎波里郊外的營地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及斯里蘭卡島的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是昨天才剛到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個自稱克拉瑪的男人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉瑪?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那個觀賞席
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有直升機來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是來把我們一網打盡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經沒有武器了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到極限了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修一修的話應該能動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你要獨自去對抗汞合金嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瘋了 那是死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們奪走了我最寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是傭兵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不是傭兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已經分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說爆了個大冷門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計已經有人準備連夜逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒備森嚴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良 你正在看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走出來 扔掉武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就殺了這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得東京那次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你應該知道我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你10秒鐘考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鳥
